name: Ms. Dynamite
description: '''Naomi Arleen McLean-Daley''' {{post-nominals|size=100%|country=GBR|MBE}} (born 26 April 1981), better known as '''Ms. Dynamite''', is a British singer and rapper. She is the recipient of the [[Mercury Prize|Mercury Music Prize]], two [[Brit Awards]] and three [[MOBO Awards]].
